      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>halved cherry</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 2-3 min</p><p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse your <strong>green lentils</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1606826117417-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1606826117417-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1606826117417-x700.jpg",
