          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1606826117417-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained lentils</strong>, <strong>dried basil</strong>,<strong> soft cheese</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>cider vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to the pan</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until the mixture has slightly thickened</p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your<strong> creamy lentil & tomato filling</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-1606826240396-x200.jpg",
