            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, remove the<strong> softened flat white mushrooms</strong> from the grill and discard any excess mushroom liquid</p><p>Add the <strong>creamy lentil & tomato filling</strong> to the mushrooms and sprinkle the <strong>grated cheese</strong> over the top – these are your <strong>stuffed flat white mushrooms</strong></p><p>Return the <strong>stuffed flat white mushrooms</strong> to the grill for 3-4 min or until the cheese has melted – these are your<strong> cheesy lentil & tomato stuffed flat white mushrooms</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
