            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are under the grill, combine the <strong>remaining cider vinegar </strong>and a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> in a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
