    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cheesy lentil & tomato stuffed flat white mushrooms</strong> with the<strong> salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>dressing </strong>over the salad<strong> </strong>and garnish with your <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
